Improvements
============
 - make xml.context cache documents during spidering for speed.
 - try using mmap in the FileHandler for speed
 - move __strptime from the various XPath extensions into util.date.
 - actually, util.date is pretty much inauspicious.org specific and can
   be nobbled when the handlers are moved away.

